=<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Blue Horizon Finance — Not Eligible</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;600;700&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  :root {
    --navy: #1A1A2E; --red: #C0392B; --cream: #FAF8F3; --white: #FFFFFF;
    --text-dark: #1A2634; --text-mid: #4A5568; --text-light: #718096; --border: #E2E8F0;
  }
  body { font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; background: #EEF2F7; color: var(--text-dark); padding: 40px 20px; }
  .email-shell { max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; background: var(--white); border-radius: 2px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(11,31,58,0.12); }
  .email-header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1A1A2E 0%, #2D1B3D 60%, #4A2550 100%); padding: 40px 48px 36px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .email-header::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: -40px; right: -40px; width: 200px; height: 200px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(192,57,43,0.1); }
  .logo-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .logo-icon { width: 44px; height: 44px; background: #C9A84C; border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 22px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .logo-text { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; color: #fff; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.2; }
  .logo-tagline { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .header-badge { display: inline-block; padding: 5px 14px; border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,100,100,0.5); border-radius: 2px; color: #FFB3B3; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .email-header h1 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; color: #fff; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.3; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .accent-bar { height: 4px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #8B0000, var(--red), #8B0000); }
  .email-body { padding: 40px 48px; }
  .salutation { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-dark); margin-bottom: 16px; text-transform: uppercase }
  .body-text { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--text-mid); margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .body-text strong { color: var(--text-dark); font-weight: 600; }
  .info-card { background: var(--cream); border-left: 4px solid var(--red); border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0; padding: 20px 24px; margin: 28px 0; }
  .info-card-title { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-light); margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .info-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 14px; }
  .info-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .info-label { color: var(--text-mid); }
  .info-value { color: var(--text-dark); font-weight: 600; text-transform: capitalize; }
  .info-value.red { color: var(--red); }
  .alert-box { border-radius: 4px; padding: 16px 20px; margin: 24px 0; display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: flex-start; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; }
  .alert-box.danger { background: #FDF2F2; border: 1px solid #F5C6CB; color: var(--red); }
  .alert-icon { font-size: 18px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
  .cta-wrap { text-align: center; margin: 32px 0; }
  .cta-btn { display: inline-block; padding: 14px 40px; background: #6B2D6B; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.05em; border-radius: 3px; }
  .signature { margin-top: 36px; padding-top: 24px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-mid); line-height: 1.7; }
  .sig-name { font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-dark); font-size: 15px; }
  .sig-role { color: var(--text-light); font-size: 13px; }
  .email-footer { background: #1A1A2E; padding: 28px 48px; text-align: center; }
  .footer-text { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.7; }
  .footer-links { margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .footer-links a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px; font-size: 11px; }
  @media (max-width: 600px) { .email-header, .email-body, .email-footer { padding: 28px 24px; } .email-header h1 { font-size: 22px; } }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="email-shell">
  <div class="email-header">
    <div class="logo-row">
      <div class="logo-icon">🌊</div>
      <div>
        <div class="logo-text">Blue Horizon Finance</div>
        <div class="logo-tagline">Trusted Lending Solutions</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="header-badge">Application Status Update</div>
    <h1>Regarding Your<br>Loan Application</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="accent-bar"></div>
  <div class="email-body">
    <p class="salutation">Dear {{ $('Store CRM Data').item.json.Name }},</p>
    <p class="body-text">Thank you for your interest in a loan with <strong>Blue Horizon Finance</strong>. After a thorough review of your application, we regret to inform you that we are <strong>unable to proceed</strong> with your request at this time.</p>
    <div class="info-card">
      <div class="info-card-title">Application Review Details</div>
      <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">Applicant</span><span class="info-value">{{ $('Store CRM Data').item.json.Name }}</span></div>
      <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">Loan Amount Requested</span><span class="info-value">{{ $('Store CRM Data').item.json['Loan Amount'] }}</span></div>
      <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">Salary Range</span><span class="info-value">{{ $('Store CRM Data').item.json['Salary Range'] }}</span></div>
      <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">Decision</span><span class="info-value red">Not Eligible</span></div>
    </div>
    <p class="body-text">Based on our current lending criteria, your application does not meet the minimum eligibility requirements. This decision may be influenced by factors such as income level relative to the requested loan amount, credit profile, or existing financial obligations.</p>
    <div class="alert-box danger">
      <span class="alert-icon">⚠️</span>
      <span><strong>What you can do:</strong> You may reapply after 6 months if your financial circumstances change, or explore our smaller loan products which may be more suitable for your current profile.</span>
    </div>
    <p class="body-text">We understand this may be disappointing. Our team is available to discuss alternative financial solutions that may better fit your current situation. Please do not hesitate to contact us.</p>
    <div class="cta-wrap"><a href="#" class="cta-btn">Speak to an Advisor</a></div>
    <div class="signature">
      <div class="sig-name">Credit Assessment Team</div>
      <div class="sig-role">Blue Horizon Finance</div>
      <div>📞 +1 (800) 274-5678 &nbsp;|&nbsp; 🌐 www.bluehorizonfinance.com</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="email-footer">
    <div class="footer-links">
      <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a><a href="#">Terms of Service</a><a href="#">Contact Us</a><a href="#">Unsubscribe</a>
    </div>
    <p class="footer-text">© 2025 Blue Horizon Finance. All rights reserved.<br>123 Finance Avenue, Suite 500, New York, NY 10001</p>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>

